        "overview": {
          "base": "You enchant an area no larger than 30 feet in any direction. Creatures within this area that are lower <a href=\"https://wiki.teriock.com/index.php/Core:Leveling_Up\" title=\"Core:Leveling Up\" target=\"_blank\">level</a> than you cannot knowingly lie. Any other creature must make a <a href=\"https://wiki.teriock.com/index.php/Tradecraft:Courtier\" title=\"Tradecraft:Courtier\" target=\"_blank\">courtier check</a> with a DC equal to the difference between your <a href=\"https://wiki.teriock.com/index.php/Core:Leveling_Up\" title=\"Core:Leveling Up\" target=\"_blank\">level</a> and theirs when they enter. If they fail, they cannot knowingly lie. You do not know the results of the check.",
